# Landing Page Redesign — Click2PDF

Redesign the [index.html](file:///e:/project/click2pdf/public/index.html) landing page from its current cartoon/playful style into a **modern, professional, high-conversion SaaS landing page** with premium aesthetics, smooth animations, and clear value propositions.

## Design Direction

- **Dark-to-light gradient hero** with glassmorphism elements
- **Inter** font (clean, modern SaaS standard) replacing Quicksand
- Refined color palette: deep navy `#0f172a`, electric blue `#3b82f6`, vibrant violet `#8b5cf6`, fresh teal `#06b6d4`
- Subtle micro-animations (fade-in on scroll, floating elements, gradient text)
- Professional copy that communicates trust and capability
- Still uses **Tailwind CDN** (matching current stack) — no build step change

## Proposed Changes

### Landing Page

#### [MODIFY] [index.html](file:///e:/project/click2pdf/public/index.html)

Complete rewrite of the HTML body while preserving:
- All SEO meta tags, structured data, and OpenGraph tags
- Auth module import ([js/auth.js](file:///e:/project/click2pdf/public/js/auth.js)) and service worker registration
- Pricing modal content & logic
- Footer links (Privacy, Returns, Refunds, Disclaimer, Contact, Help)

**New sections (top to bottom):**

1. **Navbar** — Sticky glass-effect navbar with logo, nav links (Features, How It Works, Pricing), and "Get Started" CTA button
2. **Hero** — Full-width gradient background, large headline with gradient text, animated subtext, dual CTAs ("Start Free" + "See How It Works"), floating decorative shapes, and a subtle animated demo mockup area
3. **Trusted By / Social Proof** — Stats bar showing key metrics (e.g., "10,000+ PDFs Processed", "99.9% Uptime", "100% Secure")
4. **Features Grid** — 6 feature cards with icons, titles, and descriptions showcasing: Form Filling, Bulk Fill, PDF Merge, PDF Split, PDF Conversion, Security
5. **How It Works** — Redesigned 3-step process with numbered cards, connector lines, and clean icons (Upload → Edit → Download)
6. **Security / Trust** — Modern trust section with glassmorphism card, shield icon, encryption & auto-delete badges
7. **Pricing Section** (inline, not just modal) — Clean 3-column pricing cards visible on the page, with the existing modal as a backup
8. **Final CTA** — Gradient CTA banner with compelling headline
9. **Footer** — Modern multi-column footer with logo, links, and copyright

**Technical details:**
- CSS-only scroll-reveal animations using `IntersectionObserver`
- Gradient text via `background-clip: text`
- Glassmorphism via `backdrop-filter: blur()` + semi-transparent backgrounds
- Responsive: fully mobile-optimized with proper spacing

